      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a social media expert.\n\nBased on the following blog:\n\n{{ $json.text || $json.output || JSON.stringify($json) }}\n\nCreate:\n\n1. A LinkedIn post (150–250 words with emojis and hashtags)\n\n2. A Twitter/X post (under 280 characters)\n\nReturn in this format:\n\nLinkedIn:\n...\n\nTwitter:\n...",
